# Material.Avalonia 控件使用指南

> **命名空间声明（在 UserControl 顶部添加）**
> ```xml
> xmlns:material="using:Material.Styles.Controls"
> xmlns:icons="clr-namespace:Material.Icons.Avalonia;assembly=Material.Icons.Avalonia"
> xmlns:assists="clr-namespace:Material.Styles.Assists;assembly=Material.Styles"
> ```

---

## 1. 排版 Typography

`TextBlock` 通过 `Classes` 设定 Material 字体样式，无需额外引用。

| Class | 大小 | 用途 |
|---|---|---|
| `Headline1` | 96sp Light | 超大标题 |
| `Headline2` | 60sp Light | 大标题 |
| `Headline3` | 48sp Regular | 页面主标题 |
| `Headline4` | 34sp Regular | 区域标题（页面级） |
| `Headline5` | 24sp Regular | 卡片标题 |
| `Headline6` | 20sp Medium | 子标题 |
| `Subtitle1` | 16sp Regular | 正文小标题 |
| `Subtitle2` | 14sp Medium | 次级小标题 |
| `Body1` | 16sp Regular | 正文主体 |
| `Body2` | 14sp Regular | 正文辅助 |
| `Caption` | 12sp Regular | 说明文字 |
| `Overline` | 10sp Regular | 上标签 |
| `ButtonText` | 14sp Medium | 按钮文字 |

```xml
<TextBlock Classes="Headline4 Subheadline" Text="区域标题" />
<TextBlock Classes="Headline6" Text="卡片标题" />
<TextBlock Classes="Body2" Text="说明文字" />
<TextBlock Classes="Caption" Text="辅助提示" />
```

> `Subheadline` / `Subheadline2` 是额外的间距辅助类，常与 Headline4/Headline6 配合使用。

